title: Aerolyn - Resilience
description:
Aerolyn is a post-hardcore band from Omaha that only released two albums. One EP and one full length. Although they didn't last long, with their two releases they have left us post-hardcore fans something that will last forever. Resilience is their debut EP and it features guest vocals from Jonny Craig and Kellin Quinn.

Bit Rate: 192kpbs

Track Listing:
1. Between Lions and Men
2. The Demolisher
3. Interlude
4. Harbinger feat. Jonny Craig
5. The Architect
6. WeFightFail feat. Kellin Quinn
7. Resilience
